This course, designed by Charles Czeisler, professor of sleep medicine at Harvard Medical School and specialist at Brigham and Women's Hospital, is in his opinion the first of the kind in the United States.
It was after giving a lecture on the effects of sleep deprivation on learning that the idea came to her
